EXTERN

NAME
   extern - declaring a external function or variable

SYNOPSIS
    If can't find a function or variable in front of current complied statement, 
    it will also be found in the back of the current file or in other files.

DESCRIPTION
    Modern compliers always has compile and link two steps. 
    
    Compiler compiles source file sperately and generates object code file.
    So, when compiles a file, complier don't know other files content.
    
    
